replies.body: Hi Chao, Can you tell us what is the error? Did you check the outputs of ReadMe?
attached pic shows the readme panel

Did you try copying in the new libraries the ReadMe suggests? I can't read the text in the image, but if it's the same issue I've had previously (at Mostapha's suggestion) I copied the new "CSharp" DLL's over into my Ladybug directory structure, and the OS generator started working (again).
I second Nick's comment and also suggest you to share your file if the problem persists.
